data.description: Situated on a quiet cul-de-sac in the desirable Fieldstone neighborhood, this spacious home offers 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. The open concept kitchen with appliances included and dining room is perfect for family gatherings and entertaining. Upstairs features a master bedroom with vaulted ceilings, a large walk-in closet, and a master bathroom with a jetted tub for ultimate relaxation. Enjoy evenings on the covered front porch or head to the back patio with a covered pergola that stays with the house! Property also includes 2 outdoor storage sheds. Home is being sold as is with immediate possession. Schedule your showing today!
